description.narrative: Health and government institutions at different levels have enhanced capacities and financial resources to effectively implement evidence-based immunization services., which contributes to Child Health, Child Health (Covid), Immunization, Immunization (Covid). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Evaluations, Research And Data, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2025, children benefit from quality, evidence-based and integrated health, nutrition and early childhood development systems
